query:
-- Atualizar pickingOrderId com base nas reservas
UPDATE pickingWaveItems pwi
JOIN inventory inv ON (
  pwi.locationId = inv.locationId 
  AND pwi.productId = inv.productId 
  AND pwi.batch = inv.batch
)
JOIN pickingReservations pr ON inv.id = pr.inventoryId
SET pwi.pickingOrderId = pr.pickingOrderId
WHERE pwi.waveId = 30004 AND pwi.pickingOrderId IS NULL;
